title: LF Diamond 4 and up ranked duo partner
body:
Hi, 
I am looking for a duo partner to play with.
I keep getting demoted back to plat due to inactivity and would really appreciate someone to duo with to give me an enjoyable incentive to play ranked.
please add me in game if your keen.
I am a mid/adc player. i can fill pretty well anywhere with the exception of having a limited jungle champion pool.
